claim.claim-text:
An image display apparatus, comprising:
a display unit including a display surface that is capable of displaying a real space;
a detector that detects an azimuth of the display unit around at least one axis;
a region limiter that is capable of limiting a display region of the field of view along a direction of the one axis in three-dimensional coordinates surrounding the display unit;
a storage unit that stores images that should be displayed in the field of view with the images being made corresponding to the three-dimensional coordinates; and
a display control unit that displays, based on an output of the detector, an image in the three-dimensional coordinates, which corresponds to the azimuth, in the field of view.
